既幾個鐘, 麻醉藥過左之後,<br />\n手指條骨就開始慢慢痛, 真係體驗到十指痛歸心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左第一晚之後都冇咩野架喇<br />\n(之後條路就個個人唔同)<br />\n我case係咁: <br />\n大慨9個月後, 我就再做多次手術拆番出黎<br />\n好快搞掂, ~30min<br />\n不過做完手術都唔太靈活<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}